      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ある日の仕事の帰り道",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Way back home from work one day",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 1333.3333691,
          "startTime": 1.3333333691
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "……ふふふ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ha-ha-ha",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.5333332698,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "千紗？\nやけに上機嫌だが何かいいことでもあったのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa?\nYou seem to be in a particularly good mood. Did something good happen?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.3333330154,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 9.3131061434
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、すみません\n星見まつりのことを考えてたら、つい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ sorry.\nI was just thinking about the Hoshimi festival…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.4131061434,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "今年の星見まつりのステージに、サニーピースが\n出演することになりましたよね。それが嬉しくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This year‚ Sunny Peace will be performing on\nthe Hoshimi festival‚ right? That makes me so happy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.2131060163,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.0131055076
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "サニピは星見市で生まれたグループだから\n雫ちゃんとも「凱旋ライブだね」って話してたんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sunny Peace was born in Hoshimi City‚ so…\nShizuku-chan and I were talking about how it's like a homecoming live.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.746438841,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 31.946438841
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そんなに喜ぶなんて\n千紗は星見まつりに思い入れがあるのか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're that excited about it?\nDo you have a special attachment to the Hoshimi festival?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.9666660945,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 37.084806164
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "はい、お父さんが星見まつりが好きで\n子供の頃によく連れて行ってもらったんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes‚ my dad loves the Hoshimi festival.\nWhen I was a child‚ he often took me there.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.8514728307,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんと浴衣を着て\nお父さんと一緒に屋台を回って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My sister and I would wear yukatas and…\nWe would go around the stalls with our dad…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.8848079442,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.6848076899
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_07_01-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "家族みんなで流星群を見て帰るのが\n私の夏の楽しみでした",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Watching the meteor shower with my family before going home…\nThat was my summer delight.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.4848076899,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}